gnutls_heartbeat_allowed(3)                                                                       gnutls                                                                       gnutls_heartbeat_allowed(3)

NAME
       gnutls_heartbeat_allowed - API function

SYNOPSIS
       #include <gnutls/gnutls.h>

       unsigned gnutls_heartbeat_allowed(gnutls_session_t session, unsigned int type);

ARGUMENTS
       gnutls_session_t session
                   is a gnutls_session_t type.

       unsigned int type
                   one of GNUTLS_HB_LOCAL_ALLOWED_TO_SEND and GNUTLS_HB_PEER_ALLOWED_TO_SEND

DESCRIPTION
       This function will check whether heartbeats are allowed to be sent or received in this session.

RETURNS
       Non zero if heartbeats are allowed.

SINCE
       3.1.2

REPORTING BUGS
       Report bugs to <bugs@gnutls.org>.
       Home page: https://www.gnutls.org

